short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Free AI Voice is a Chrome browser extension that utilizes Text-to-Speech (TTS) technology to convert web page articles into speech.

long.ar:
Free AI Voice is a Chrome browser extension that utilizes Text-to-Speech (TTS) technology to convert web page articles into speech and provides support for over 40 languages.
It is suitable for various websites, including news sites, blogs, fan fiction, publications, textbooks, school and classroom sites, as well as online university course materials.

Free AI Voice allows you to choose from multiple TTS voices, including those provided by the browser. Some cloud-based voices may require additional in-app purchases to activate.

Free AI Voice is suitable for those who prefer listening to content rather than reading, have dyslexia or other learning disabilities, and children who are learning to read.

ğŸ‘‰ Usage:
â— First select the text you want it to read.
â— Then click the icon to start listening.
â— When it is ready to read, the number of sentences is shown on the icon.
â— To stop listening at any time click pause.

ğŸ‘‰ Note:
After installation, you may need to restart Chrome for Free AI Voice to function correctly.
